# user-service

Service quan ly nguoi dung va xac thuc (JWT) cho he thong microservices.

## Chuc nang hien tai

- Dang ky tai khoan: `POST /api/users/register`
- Dang nhap: `POST /api/users/login`
- Lay danh sach user (can token): `GET /api/users`
- Lay chi tiet user theo ID (can token): `GET /api/users/:id`
- Health check: `GET /health`

## Chay service

Tu thu muc `services/user-service`:

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Mac dinh service chay o cong `3001`.

## Bien moi truong can thiet

Tao file `.env` (hoac cung cap qua Docker) voi cac bien:

```env
PORT=3001

DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=user_service_db
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=postgres

JWT_SECRET=your-secret-key
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=24h
```

## Database

- File khoi tao schema: `init.sql`
- Ket noi Postgres duoc cau hinh trong `db.js`

## Vi du API

Dang ky:

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/users/register \
	-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
	-d '{"name":"Test User","email":"test@example.com","password":"123456","phone":"0123456789"}'
```

Dang nhap:

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/users/login \
	-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
	-d '{"email":"test@example.com","password":"123456"}'
```

Lay danh sach user (thay `<TOKEN>` bang token nhan duoc sau login):

```bash
curl http://localhost:3001/api/users \
	-H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>"
```
